Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Riverpoint’s central location offers quick and easy access to multiple major traffic arteries in the metro area including MLK Parkway, SE 14th Street, Fleur Drive and I-235 to name a few.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: 501 SW 7th Street is a single-story office/flex building with drive-up free surface parking located in Downtown Des Moines’ vibrant Riverpoint district.  The building is directly adjacent to a variety of new living and retail amenities as well as multiple public transit routes, which allows for quick and easy access to area activities and businesses.  501 SW 7th Street has professional office finish on glass and warehouse area with a dock high overhead door.
